des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your "korex" products. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our “korex home” app in app market then register an account;
(2). Configure our devices in our “korex home” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4). Search “korex home” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5). Enable “korex home” skill, and you'll be navigated to “korex home” login page;
(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7). Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, turn on the Coffee Maker
Alexa, turn off the Coffee Maker
Alexa, turn on the Warm air blower
Alexa, turn off the Warm air blower
Alexa, what is the temperature on the Warm air blower?
Alexa, turn on the light
Alexa, set light to green
